{{Infobox Journal | title = Solar Energy Materials and Solar Cells | cover = Solar Energy Materials and Solar Cells.gif | abbreviation = Sol. Energy Mater Sol. Cells | discipline = [[Solar cell]]s | editor = C. M. Lampert | website = http://www.elsevier.com/wps/find/journaldescription.cws_home/505675/description#description | publisher = [[Elsevier]] | country = The [[Netherlands]] | history = 1968-present | link1 = http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/journal/09270248 | link1-name = Online access | eISSN = | ISSN = 0927-0248 | impact = 4.784 | impact-year = 2016 | frequency = Monthly | RSS = http://rss.sciencedirect.com/publication/science/5773 }} '''''Solar Energy Materials and Solar Cells''''' is a [[scientific journal]] published by [[Elsevier]] covering research related to [[solar energy]] materials and [[solar cells]].
